nl.tue.geometrycore.geometry.curved

Class Circle

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.tue.geometrycore.geometry.BaseGeometry<TActual>
      • nl.tue.geometrycore.geometry.CyclicGeometry<Circle>
        • nl.tue.geometrycore.geometry.curved.Circle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GeometryConvertable<Circle>

    public class Circle
extends CyclicGeometry<Circle>
    A simple circle. Note that, although it inherits from CyclicGeometry, it has no clear orientation. Thus, the computed area will always be positive.
